          { question: "Is there a customs check returning from Andorra?", answer: "Yes, French customs conduct random checks at Pas de la Case. Respect legal allowances: 300 cigarettes, 1.5L spirits, 5L wine per person." },
          { question: "Can we stop at Ax-les-Thermes on the way?", answer: "Yes, a stop at Ax thermal baths (Bains du Couloubret, €17) is possible. Allow 1h break. The free open-air Bassin des Ladres is a quick 15 min alternative." }
