          { question: "What is the best season to visit?", answer: "Spring (April-June) for flowers and light, autumn (September-October) for colours. Summer is beautiful but very busy. In winter, the village is near-deserted and mysterious." },
          { question: "Can I go canoeing on the Lot?", answer: "Yes, the Saint-Cirq to Bouzies descent (1h30, easy) is spectacular. The driver drops you upstream and collects you downstream. Ideal in summer." }
